2. Stress
The next questions ask about your feelings and thoughts during THE LAST MONTH. In each case, you will be asked to indicate how often you felt or thought a certain way. Although some of the questions are similar, there are differences between them and you should treat each one as a separate question. The best approach is to answer each question fairly quickly. Don't try to count up the number of times you felt a particular way, but rather select the answer that you think best fits for you. In the last month, how often have you:
